{"tid":953990,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救 急] bb貓唔肯食嘢","createTime":"2018-12-24T10:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T08:54:17.000Z","uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51c610963f8d975807cbeb52f3dcf760fdf23f0a","tid":953990,"uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"話說早兩日接咗兩個月大嘅貓仔返屋企<br />\n番去嘅車程都好生猛 跳跳紮<br />\n去到獸醫body check都完全冇事 <br />\n返到屋企有飲水有食曬啲糧<br />\n有柯屎柯尿 玩得好癲<br />\n今朝起身都玩咗好耐 有飲水去廁所<br />\n但係！佢唔肯食嘢呀TT 上一次食係琴晚凌晨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獸醫未覆最快幾時有booking<br />\n有冇貓奴遇過呢啲情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7d7045290a1df3cb02b0849d0181f62ff3e226","tid":953990,"uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"😿"},{"pid":"7b71b689baa393ebefb3b781a7518672d6bca379","tid":953990,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"試下餵羊奶粉溝糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f239d2976bd1b0b1aa5b8208dbb8e9ff7e4caecc","tid":953990,"uid":16985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"我隻仔岩岩番黎1-2個個陣都係咁<br />\ncheck哂所有野都唔知咩事<br />\n咩都唔食(小食,禁,雞肉,罐頭)<br />\n之後用針筒餵佢食小小野<br />\n過左幾日就正常番<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗左成皮野都唔安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd2649745f647798fd86227f3c6d76423629634","tid":953990,"uid":162330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"雞肉引誘佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as